messages.content:
Create a one day travel itinerary for the city of Sydney. Include popular attractions, good places to eat, and fun activities. Make it concise and easy to follow. Output the itinerary in a list format with each item starting with a bullet point. For example: 
• Visit the Eiffel Tower
• Lunch at a local cafe
• Explore the Louvre Museum
• Dinner at a Michelin-star restaurant
